title: Darn Tough Men's Steely Boot Midweight with Full Cushion Toe Box Work Sock (Style 2006) -
description: Midweight with Cushion - A warm and extremely comfortable choice when conditions demand it, this fine gauge knitted sock provides mid-level cushion density under your foot. True Seamless technology allows for an undetectable seam fusion for an ultra-smooth, invisible feel.
Boot Sock Height - Sits mid-calf for added protection and warmth. A sturdy companion.

Composition - Knit with 56% Merino Wool 41% Nylon 3% Lycra Spandex. The fast action wicking pulls moisture away from skin, so no more sweaty, stinky socks. The soft, breathable merino wool has fast drying, all weather performance that keeps you cool in the summer and warm in the winter.
Guaranteed for Life - If these socks wear, tear, or develop holes, Darn Tough will replace them. No strings. No conditions.
Made in the USA - Every pair of socks is knit in Vermont - the perfect testing ground for the finest premium all weather performance socks.
Darn Tough 2006-C-D021-04 Steely Boot Midweight with Cushion w/ Full Cushion Toe Box Timber Medium
